[{"Code":"en","Title":"BCA Switcher Direct","Slug":"draft-bca-switcher-direct","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj4-rm1h8k-254\"><a id=\"_j5wih1vxvjn6\" display=\"false\"></a></p><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj4-2mpo5f-255\"><a id=\"_df9ij9biwbs1\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj4-3dp2y1-256\"><a id=\"_9j6h54imkhti\" display=\"false\"></a>Glossary</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj5-uvpvp8-257\"><strong>Terms</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj5-4tyrtf-258\"><strong>Description</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj5-egae4l-259\">AM</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj6-ncj2m9-260\">Account Manager</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj6-ytaowc-261\">BAT</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj6-jbew8z-262\">Berita Acara Testing</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj6-puw3w6-263\">Cashpay</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj6-iko0a4-264\">Xendit’s product team that handles VA</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj7-8vmv4w-265\">UAT</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj7-yzvg1q-266\">User Acceptance Test</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj7-rm2r9g-267\">Company Code</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj7-wczayi-268\">5 digit Unique number from BCA for each merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj7-osgi8y-269\">Fixed Bill</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj7-ccn99j-270\">User will pay exact amount from the bill</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj8-3wj3y9-271\">No Bill</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj8-4k7k5g-272\">User will input the amount to pay the bill</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj8-bpn560-273\"><a id=\"_cgq5oqxzdqds\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj8-qpq6ak-274\"><a id=\"_ejxly55we75x\" display=\"false\"></a>Xendit Stakeholders</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj8-156v6l-275\"><strong>Department</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj8-v5vrco-276\"><strong>PIC</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj8-x98kva-277\"><strong>PIC Role</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj9-c0q89y-278\">Partnership</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj9-4wyaeg-279\"><a><u>Anggis Dinda</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj9-tpm7af-280\">Partnership PIC for BCA</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj9-53eb61-281\">Cashpay</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj9-7eskcw-282\"><a><u>Raditya Reza Ariobimo</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj9-sy3c01-283\">Product Manager (Virtual Account)</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xj9-mjc457-284\"><a id=\"_39xdf4x96zrc\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xja-cspvc6-285\"><a id=\"_ctddxe6fxgu9\" display=\"false\"></a>Eligibility</h2><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xja-8u887s-286\"><a id=\"_audslu4b8jx\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xja-k9qly1-287\"><strong>Entity Type</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xja-2v95dk-288\"><strong>Can Apply for BCA VA Switcher Direct?</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xja-vjve3w-289\">Indonesian Entity (PT/CV/Yayasan)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xja-04uly5-290\">✅</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjb-isrlkk-291\">Indonesian Entity (Perseroan perorangan/PP)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjb-lkbsk6-292\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjb-4rs6gd-293\">Indonesian Individual</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjb-zov1dm-294\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjb-9vfgnd-295\">Foreign Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjb-dc96nv-296\">❌</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjc-d1d5fj-297\">Foreign Individual</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjc-th31s6-298\">❌</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjc-lueq1f-299\"><a id=\"_92n9su4tgnow\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjc-0nkr4k-300\"><a id=\"_acexhig5p7db\" display=\"false\"></a>Industry Restriction</h2><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjc-vl3w1l-301\"><em>*) notes: there were some exceptions made if sales are really pushing for this. MO will to coordinate with partnership for partnerships to negotiate with partner</em></p><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjc-vhof4k-302\"><a id=\"_opno5zvq83i1\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjc-dg9xjy-303\"><strong>Industry</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjc-yj8idq-304\"><strong>List of Business</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"5\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjc-zofv8g-305\">Pornographic/adult services/night club</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjd-ndurfo-306\">Sale of dangerous products/services, i.e. weaponry, illegal drugs, and narcotics</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjd-d1ftfn-307\">Gambling</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjd-5fjywr-308\">Sale of fake/imitated goods in which breaches the intellectual/property rights</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjd-zg5cpu-309\">Merchants that indicated/suspected as platform offering illegal cash-out (gesek tunai/gestun)</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjd-g7lfbs-310\">Jasa Titip</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"5\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjd-5mgumv-311\">Financial institutions</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xje-0g8xfc-312\">Banks and Remittance</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xje-gilxfp-313\">Peer to Peer lending without license/not registered in Otoritas Jasa Keuangan (OJK)</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xje-cqyrpb-314\">Payment Gateway or business that can potentially act as an aggregator</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xje-ckjzsx-315\">Merchants classified as Financial Tech or Digital Finance companies without Bank Indonesia license</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xje-ibrghv-316\">Merchants classified as Financial Tech companies without license/not registered in OJK</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"3\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xje-z2fi62-317\">Non-financial businesses that require licensing</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjf-we4jgz-318\">Sale of alcohol/liquor/booze without license</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjf-ep09cs-319\">Sale of living creatures without license i.e breeder, kennel, adoption center</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjf-llvilz-320\">Business which product/services is yet to be licensed by authorities</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjf-cjy0z9-321\"><a id=\"_w2g1ajchr0f\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmkah26d-yw1k22-392\"><a id=\"_6c0oxkffxx60\" display=\"false\"></a>Merchant Requirements </h2><p data-block-id=\"mmkahaor-ztn1r6-395\">Below are the requirements that a merchant has to submit, whether ir’s upon onboarding or VA application request</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mmkah26d-874m1t-393\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjf-wo3l12-325\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-8h2zs9o5.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></h2><p data-block-id=\"mmkahvn3-fjvtpp-396\">Prior to the onboarding process, here are the list of documents required for a merchant to attach:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjf-rv8yu5-327\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-8h9pev-328\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jy-wg3s7q-346\">Form BCA VA </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-213wn9-329\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jy-npxq04-347\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/18XHJCmGhAJTj3PjqMd_WDw5ItYuT00kY/view?usp=drive_link\"><u>Form terbaru 2024</u></a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-wbqao1-330\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jy-gwfq1g-348\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/17wEfmUNj47RBoPR60qoc7Fnz4_ISFyhM/view?usp=sharing\"><u>Ketentuan BCA VA</u></a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-a9xa1k-331\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jy-ta542h-349\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1fr8ILPCMjH-3bb1j2jIw2Ze1yGmTHGBc/view?usp=sharing\"><u>RIPLAY</u></a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-57tgac-332\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jy-gmotci-350\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1GXd226sKWsxRaG1tVhXQgTbIwnMmx0rL/view?usp=sharing\"><u>Petunjuk pengisian</u></a>  </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-4lk8y6-333\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jy-d46zhl-351\">Legal Document </p><ol data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-dpnwdg-334\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-pbuqjg-335\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jy-40z8rv-352\">NPWP company</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-e9psxa-336\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jy-plbt4v-353\">Deed of Company’s Establishment or Newest Deed</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-fsz28g-337\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jy-au0y2t-354\">SK Menkeh based on Akta</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-8xxrdc-338\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jz-5zenlf-355\">TDP &amp; SIUP or NIB</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-9pdg73-339\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jz-3edu5f-356\">Director’s Identity Card</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-vlind2-340\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jz-f3a6fl-357\">Website</p><ol data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-dvja88-341\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-9kw0sc-342\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jz-uk1m2o-358\">No Social Media and Micro-Ecommerce / e-commerce</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-x8n6s7-343\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jz-grix67-359\">If a website, website must be active and fully running, i.e:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-ryz0qt-344\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-k93da6-345\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jz-0l08m2-360\">Link is accessible</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-0wprh1-346\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jz-9q3le7-361\">Show product/ service</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-0b4sdk-347\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jz-fjuj89-362\">Price in IDR</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-qhucwr-348\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jz-2aak6l-363\">Not a template or “coming soon” website</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-n5jal7-349\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6jz-jynfww-364\">If an app, app is listed in PlayStore / AppStore</p></li></ol></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-ahliq3-350\"><a id=\"_ujkex4eg0uw0\" display=\"false\"></a>SLA</h2><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjg-fct30d-351\">BCA VA Switcher Direct activated in <strong>14 working days</strong> from the date merchant submits complete requirements to MO</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjh-3nnw90-352\"><a id=\"_r0miqi6pvfyc\" display=\"false\"></a>Onboarding Flow</h2><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjh-ofrzzu-353\"><a id=\"_m5b14r4s1l6z\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjh-kwct50-354\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjh-81ikic-355\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjh-jzidci-356\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjh-6f2vxk-357\"><strong>Owner</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjh-x689xe-358\">Merchant applies for BCA VA</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xji-5my0c3-359\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xji-q0e582-360\">AM/Sales fill the <strong><em>BCA VA Switcher Tracker </em></strong>for non-crypto merchant and AM/Sales fill in <strong><em>BCA VA Crypto Tracker</em> </strong>for crypto merchant<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1IdpkBc8lSJgPdCXvbCB6xyNeYcoc1PbsThxTyoHiZ4k/edit?resourcekey#gid=1466911342\"><u>XENDIT - BCA VA Registration Form (Responses)</u></a> </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xji-wbeb8k-361\">Sales/AM</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"9\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xji-38qqf7-362\">MO Process Merchant’s Application</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xji-92xtwp-363\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xji-dkl8n3-364\">MO checks <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1IdpkBc8lSJgPdCXvbCB6xyNeYcoc1PbsThxTyoHiZ4k/edit?resourcekey#gid=1466911342\"><u>XENDIT - BCA VA Registration Form (Responses)</u></a> in <em>BCA VA Switcher Tracker </em>sheet</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xji-wpf67q-365\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-24m9h4-366\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-m3o5xp-367\">MO sends form to merchant by email by filling  <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1IdpkBc8lSJgPdCXvbCB6xyNeYcoc1PbsThxTyoHiZ4k/edit?resourcekey#gid=1466911342\"><u>XENDIT - BCA VA Registration Form (Responses)</u></a> in <em>Send Form VA</em> sheet, cc-ing AM/Sales :</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-7whhym-368\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-gk79wh-369\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-nt8jl7jm.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-6r3dba-370\"><em>*)note : by filling this sheet, email will be sent automatically via Zapier along with the </em><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1g_Wta_QlVOb0EJmlfYOzJBU-ZGW7iG4JxLpee88Gpd8/edit#heading=h.x5gzec6f0lg\"><em><u>attachment</u></em></a><em> form.</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-667vwr-371\">How to fill the sheet:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-44z8fx-372\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-5ar9w0-373\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k1-yi0139-365\">Merchant name : fill with merchant business/legal name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-u6xte9-374\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k1-w2gptc-366\">Email : fill with merchant’s email</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-jzi7at-375\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k1-fh71rp-367\">Email 2 : fill with Xendit sales PIC email</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-3cpuxm-376\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k1-pscxcn-368\">Send email : choose one category either is it crypto merchant or not. </p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-junun1-377\">Email example:</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-txq9ve-378\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-2nvj47-379\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-xr039fqj.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-ab8k2k-380\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-bnk4i3-381\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-ufzv1ogj.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjj-ig6oyw-382\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjk-oomxg1-383\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjk-emvrc4-384\">After merchant fills in forms, merchant scans them and sends to <a><u>merchantops@xendit.co</u></a> by email to be reviewed</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjk-herahw-385\">Merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjk-usq0t4-386\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjk-w5s6ke-387\">MO checks the form. If the requirements are fulfilled - please follow the <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1GXd226sKWsxRaG1tVhXQgTbIwnMmx0rL/view?usp=sharing\"><u>guidelines</u></a>. MO informs merchant to send hardcopy form to :</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjk-w3a5te-388\">Xendit</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjk-n50jrh-389\">Gedung Victoria lt 3 Jl. Sultan Hasanudin No.47-51, RW.2,</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjk-oj9hpe-390\">Melawai, Kec. Kby. Baru,</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjk-j8vz49-391\">Kota Jakarta Selatan, Daerah Khusus Ibukota Jakarta 12160</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjk-i8mw5j-392\">UP: MerchantOps (BCA VA) </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjl-l0mh98-393\">Merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjl-b55pj4-394\">6</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjl-ozcmc5-395\">MO updates <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1IdpkBc8lSJgPdCXvbCB6xyNeYcoc1PbsThxTyoHiZ4k/edit?usp=sharing\"><u>XENDIT - BCA VA Registration Form (Responses)</u></a> in “Tracker send to BCA” sheet by filling the details in a new row</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjl-7w0tm9-396\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjl-bi33xn-397\">7</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjl-5pyua1-398\">MO signs and put company stamps in Lampiran Teknis form. Once done,  MO scans and uploads the softcopy form to gdrive <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1u4_eyNOCuFFPkJ1VC4LTvdLs-3bDBAC8?usp=sharing\"><u>BCA Switcher Direct filled form</u></a> </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjl-dm1i7n-399\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjm-jm12k2-400\">8</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjm-h650hm-401\">MO uploads soft copy legal docs to BCA sharing <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/0APDL1rtjeeXsUk9PVA\"><u>drive</u></a> </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjm-sa9u7i-402\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjm-0c425y-403\">9</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjm-7egsax-404\">Once done, MO prints merchant’s NPWP, AKTA, and SK and send the printed hardcopies to BCA:<br type=\"inline\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjm-ny49c3-406\">PT Bank Central Asia Tbk,</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjm-0jvrfe-407\">Divisi Pengembangan Solusi Kerjasama Transaksi Perbankan (E-Commerce Management),</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjm-zbvl7p-408\">Menara BCA Lantai 17, Grand Indonesia,</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjm-ahxd5r-409\">Jl. M.H. Thamrin No. 1,</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjm-y1rmv4-410\">Jakarta Pusat 10310</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjm-uvux70-411\">UP : Linsay (021) 23588000 ext. 1050598</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjm-2aqhkb-412\"><br type=\"inline\">Or <br type=\"inline\"><br type=\"inline\">PT Bank Central Asia Tbk,</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjn-3w0mjd-416\">Divisi Pengembangan Solusi Kerjasama Transaksi Perbankan (E-Commerce Management),</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjn-p0bu3u-417\">Menara BCA Lantai 32, Grand Indonesia,</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjn-25k31t-418\">Jl. M.H. Thamrin No. 1,</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjn-3ljom5-419\">Jakarta Pusat 10310</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjn-2kne0t-420\">UP VORA/EVALIA</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjn-eqvro2-421\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjn-kg2twd-422\">10</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjn-elu8zg-423\">BCA receives the documents and review</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjn-768fqe-424\">BCA</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjn-6cepp4-425\"><a id=\"_k5o8o77cwq5o\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjn-784lhg-426\"><a id=\"_u96tqxtduroc\" display=\"false\"></a>Activation Flow</h2><h1 data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjn-nrzwew-427\"><a id=\"_b3npbtwfzrms\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjo-uawxhw-428\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjo-9c2hat-429\"><strong>No</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjo-r7nr0w-430\"><strong>Steps</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjo-h9sihr-431\"><strong>Owner</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"4\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjo-udsntg-432\">VA Testing</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjo-b1yk65-433\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-5itoka-434\">Once approved, BCA will inform company code to MO by email</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-k873a4-435\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-9yvsgr-436\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-h620woe6.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-e68vyv-437\">BCA</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-747mqp-438\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-ecrtih-439\">Partnership/MO informs the company code to cashpay to create VA in #p-virtual-account by creating a workflow. Select VA BCA Switcher UAT Act and fill the form.</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-ds6xjc-440\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-prlkug-441\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k5-ekj0le-369\">Put the company code in the notes section</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-kxuzzn-442\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k5-ie0cat-370\">Choose the bill type as mentioned by BCA in the email (point 12)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-8akmpd-443\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-gqcuai-444\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-t7782rmk.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-2lyhrc-445\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-8vz838im.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-vqedxo-446\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-fo8lzp-447\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-ed4fdd5a.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjp-i5do1r-448\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjq-k0icoz-449\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjq-nhxzkm-450\">Cashpay creates VA and informs to MO <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1b1KnKVPO_Tb-MFiaHy7LPgKvKabl64dzZebbgGcjE3A/edit?usp=sharing\"><u>(VA Test example)</u></a> </p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjq-2bx17g-451\">For merchants with fixed bill, make sure that these options are toggled on (green) in Customer management -&gt; Business Settings:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjq-b73tpx-452\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjq-1q2ypn-453\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k5-v6ck49-371\">Fixed Virtual account</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjq-1kqwbe-454\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k5-vc75yl-372\">Invoice</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjq-72re4r-455\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjq-dwuh5k-456\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-tkr6jsaw.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjq-yqzvpr-457\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjq-n07oly-458\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-jabmud2z.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjq-ksmtbo-459\">Cashpay</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjq-vursh9-460\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjq-a0jaeo-461\">MO process UAT and BAT document <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1xqo0QMXy9EuLcTAntabCs3TqMq_dOhXH?usp=sharing\"><u>(BAT example)</u></a> </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-5gomui-462\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k6-jmj0dw-373\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-cez82v-463\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-orujxv-464\">MO requests to Fin Ops to do testing for Klik BCA bisnis in #merchantops slack channel with format :</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-t6gx6l-465\">{UAT BCA VA Direct}</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-swys1q-466\">hi @finops kindly help us to do UAT via Klik BCA Bisnis channel for Happy Fresh - Fixed Bill</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-16ss2r-467\">We need a screenshot only the last page please find here for your reference screenshoot Klik BCA Bisnis  (full with url)</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-6ekwmv-468\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-vj6yp5-469\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k6-5vppyq-374\">Kondisi Berhasil total bill amount is Rp. 10.000 380712549032394936 </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-g10ulo-470\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k6-3btn95-375\">Kondisi no VA tidak ditemukan 380712549032390000</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-5gb79f-471\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k6-qf76s5-376\">Kondisi tidak ada tagihan total bill amount is Rp. 0 380714454375641117</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-twswf2-472\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k6-qh0g7p-377\">Kondisi tagihan sudah lunas 380712549032394936</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-d1bj5h-473\">Thank you cc @phelia</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-zjs1zr-474\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-09715o-475\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-78czbg68.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjr-224qxy-476\">(<a href=\"https://xendit.slack.com/archives/CBCFG8EGP/p1622167502276500\"><u>Slack thread example</u></a>)<br type=\"inline\">Klik BCA bisnis guideline <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Af4acf8WPxuX00mWOvD_OI7VI3LrekfjZADQu0r53x4/edit?usp=sharing\"><u>Klik BCA Bisnis</u></a>  </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjs-t0806g-478\">MO &amp; FinOps</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjs-lqshlq-479\">6</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjs-ero49y-480\">Once done, MO will send BAT document to BCA via email to be reviewed</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjs-lrrmik-481\">Email :  <a><u>linsay_christine@bca.co.id</u></a></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjs-htofnk-482\">CC :      Xendit MerchantOps &lt;<a><u>merchantops@xendit.co</u></a>&gt; , Xendit Sales/AM</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjs-4ehrfc-483\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjs-thwimh-484\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-o8snhl6x.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjs-updtlo-485\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjs-nehh0a-486\">Approval from partner</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjs-xw8p1o-487\">7</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjs-k1hhjd-488\">BCA reviews and will inform for approval</p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjs-70xw59-489\"><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjs-bbbeq5-490\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-yxrntqj3.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-wptpj0-491\">BCA</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k7-v0svs7-378\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-t6ceuo-492\">MO sends email notification to merchant via this <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1jsZnA0Hk4kGPGU8OKq9n4LbP0IUCcLvzfxA8vWtZwJk/edit#gid=0\"><u>sheet</u></a></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-x3ttj7-493\"><strong><img data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-6aq96h-494\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/draft-bca-switcher-direct-image-ndjii6mb.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-o0kyof-495\"><em>*) Email will be sent automatically through Zapier</em></p><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-30ybn3-496\">How to fill the sheet : </p><ul data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-ommn2i-497\"><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-nga2x8-498\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k8-w27v3u-379\">Merchant name : fill with merchant business/legal name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-168t4z-499\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k8-bwo3fz-380\">Merchant business email : fill with merchant’s email</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-jzms2l-500\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k8-ww9gdh-381\">CC alternatif email merchant : fill with merchant’s other email (if any)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-xjwaja-501\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k8-v6oit6-382\">CC sales : fill with Xendit sales PIC</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-ml3ioe-502\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k8-54x9md-383\">CC 1 : fill with email (can be Xendit’s/merchant’s)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-4i9xo0-503\"><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k8-lit4e9-384\">Sent email? : fill with <em>yes</em> if the data filled are correct</p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmbp5xjt-0rnfpo-504\">MO</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mmkag6k8-tdfo0e-385\"></p>","SeoTitle":"BCA Switcher Direct","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"BCA VA Switcher","Slug":"bca-va-switcher","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"BCA VA Switcher","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"BCA VA Switcher","Slug":"bca-va-switcher","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"BCA VA Switcher","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"BCA VA Switcher","Slug":"bca-va-switcher","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"BCA VA Switcher","Description":null}]